                            "alt": "basic",
                            "game-obj": "Rules",
                            "aonid": 329
                        }
                    ],
                    "effect": "An explosion of magical energy\u2014stored up for the Spellstrike\u2014explodes out. All creatures in a 5-foot emanation take 1d6 damage per level of the spell, with a basic Reflex save against your spell DC. This damage is the same type the spell would have dealt, and the activation gains that trait; if the spell would have dealt multiple types of damage, choose one of them. If the damage of the explosion is mental, the save is Will instead of Reflex.",
                    "traits": [
                        {
                            "name": "Concentrate",
                            "type": "trait",
                            "alternate_link": {
                                "type": "alternate_link",
